longBusinessSummary: OPT-Sciences Corporation provides anti-glare solutions to the aerospace industry. It offers anti-glare optical coatings and panels for LCDs; LCD glass heaters; and EMI shielded glasses. The company was founded in 1956 and is headquartered in Cinnaminson, New Jersey.
